THIRD-PARTY LICENSES AND DATA SOURCES

This project uses the following open data sources:

1. UNHCR Refugee Statistics
   - Source: United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees (UNHCR)
   - License: Public Domain / Open Data
   - URL: https://www.unhcr.org/refugee-statistics/

2. ACLED Conflict Event Data
   - Source: Armed Conflict Location & Event Data Project (ACLED)
   - License: Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International (CC BY-NC 4.0)
   - URL: https://acleddata.com/

3. World Bank Indicators
   - Source: The World Bank Group
   - License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
   - URL: https://data.worldbank.org/

4. Climate and Environmental Data
   - Source: Various (NOAA, FAO, World Resources Institute)
   - License: Public Domain / Open Data

